      "name": "Long COVID - Symptoms Due to COVID-19 - Gastrointestinal (Long Form)",
      "code": "PX992011",
      "abbreviation": "PX992011",
      "description": "This protocol helps better describe and understand the patient experience and recovery of those with confirmed or suspected COVID-19, with a specific emphasis on Long COVID experience especially with gastrointestinal.",
