      "citation": "Neal C. Goldberg, Sabrina Poirier, Allison Kanas, Lisa McCorkell, Carrie Anna McGinn, Yochai Re’em, Kathi Kuehnel, Nina Muirhead, Tahlia Ruschioni, Susan Taylor-Brown & Leonard A. Jason (2022) A new clinical challenge: supporting patients coping with the long-term effects of COVID-19, Fatigue: Biomedicine, Health & Behavior, 10:4, 212-230, DOI: 10.1080/21641846.2022.2128576 [PhenX: https://www.phenxtoolkit.org/protocols/view/992011]",
